name: ella thank you cards
description:
Say thanks with these note cards featuring playful watercolor circles and distressed vintage tape.

    • Folded cards and matching dark eggplant color envelopes
    • Blank inside
    • 4 1/4" x 5 1/2" (when folded)
    • Printed using environmentally friendly offset printing and soy-based inks. Paper contains 100% post consumer fiber; envelopes contain 30% post consumer fiber. Both are Forest Steward Council (FSC) certified.
